    {
      "id": "1496258378555374",
      "score": 1,
      "review_title": "review",
      "review_description": "Has potential but still needs a lot of work. My game crashed during the tutorial and gameplay just doesnt feel that good:\n\n- Inconsistent aiming due to dynamic attach\n- Ammo system is weird; sometimes could or couldnt attach a magazine, sometimes could or couldnt fire even with a magazine attached\n- The selection of guns isnt wide either, its just a bunch of automatic close to mid-range weapons that deal mediocre damage (to my knowledge, there arent semi-automatics nor shotguns nor projectile launchers)\n\nThe tutorial should be reworked, too (and I believe it is, according to discord sneak peaks). I didn't even know I had an inventory system until well into a couple of matches.\n\nAlso all the five star reviews with nonsense writing are because this game incentivizes five star reviews.\n\nEDIT REGARDING THE FIRST DEV RESPONSE (which claimed that all these issues were fixed):\nI just checked the game out again today. I couldn't check tutorial because I cant return to it, but all three of the other issues persist, I'm not sure what youre talking about with \"all of them being fixed.\"\n\n- Pick up any weapon, then try grabbing it from anywhere else on the model (not just the secondary grip). The gun will snap towards that rotation. Furthermore, if you shake your hands, the gun rotation gets more and more off.\n- Magazines are still inconsistent. Some mags go into guns sideways, I had two mags in one gun at one point, I could fire a weapon while my friend couldnt fire the same one, etc.\n- I couldn't find any more guns, so to my knowledge the amount and variety of guns remains the same.\n\nEDIT REGARDING THE SECOND DEV RESPONSE:\ndont say all of the issues were fixed if the update that fixes them isnt even out",
      "date": 1777820454,
      "review_helpful_count": 5,
      "author_display_name": "ShadowFlame15",
      "author_alias": "ShadowFlame15",
      "developer_response": {
        "body": "Hello please try the game out in the new update and if you find out its good please change your rating",
        "date": 1779326647
      }
